> P90, 16Mb RAM,
> 2Mb PCI video card,
> EIDE (PCI) Controller with > 850 Mb HD
> 32 bit sound card
> Quad speed CDROM
> inkjet (or cheap laser) printer
> 28.8 modem
> Warp Connect with WinOS/2
